Attribution

scikms is derived from two upstream projects:

1. FeelUOwn (https://github.com/feeluown/FeelUOwn) — GPL-3.0-or-later.
   The PyQt6 application scaffold (plugin system, i18n framework, DSL/RPC
   server infrastructure, utilities, app modes) was extracted from FeelUOwn
   v5.x by stripping music-player-specific code.

2. SciKMS v3.1 / y-khoa (private) — clinical knowledge manager.
   The domain layer (SQLite schema, EBM/PICO/specialty classifiers, PDF/DOI
   /PubMed importers, figure atlas extraction) and the user-facing UX
   structure (8-page navigation, library/search/atlas/stats workflow) were
   ported from the Streamlit original to PyQt6.

UI styling uses PyQt6-Fluent-Widgets (https://github.com/zhiyiYo/PyQt-Fluent-Widgets),
which is GPL-3.0-or-later licensed.
